c: 40
v: 34
t: "Era mazima Yusuf yabajjira oluberyeberye n’obujulizi kyokka mwasigala muli mu kubuusabuusa kwebyo bye yabaleetera, okutuusa nga amaze okufa olwo nno nemugamba nti Katonda tagenda kutuma mubaka yenna luvannyuma lwe, bwatyo nno Katonda bwabuza buli oyo yenna yye eyegalabanja abuusabuusa"